body:
You don't often get email from hayden@reply.flocksafety.com. Learn why this is important <https://aka.ms/LearnAboutSenderIdentification>

Hi Brandon, 


I wanted to reach out as I haven�t seen your registration for our upcoming live webinar with Founder and CEO Garrett Langley on Wednesday at 1 p.m. ET / 10 a.m. PT.  


We will be discussing our no-cost APIs and presenting live demos of our newest AI tools, which are designed to help your agency close cases faster.  


You can save your spot here. https://email.flocksafety.com/NDQyLVdOSC0xODEAAAGYj2-4FLeeqVqnDOtUcB3pymFCA-M1B1P6wHo7bnCB3TBKDxy9cpEh-lCuDcH3v3GlnkQDL1Y=  


See you there, 


Hayden 


P.S. Have a scheduling conflict? Go ahead and register https://email.flocksafety.com/NDQyLVdOSC0xODEAAAGYj2-4FLeeqVqnDOtUcB3pymFCA-M1B1P6wHo7bnCB3TBKDxy9cpEh-lCuDcH3v3GlnkQDL1Y= , and we'll send you the recording after the event.
